        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Right to Earn a Living Act of 2021</b></p>  <p>This bill requires a state or local government, to be eligible to receive future payments from the Coronavirus Relief Fund, to certify that it will not limit the operation, hours, or occupancy of small businesses without the state or local government taking legislative action.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
